  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Today everything is done by the crow\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the leader of the opposition, said that an attempt to bring the Rajapaksas to power is underway again.",
        "The opposition leader said that it is the crow who sends the lists to appoint the ministers today and said that all the misguided members of the United National Party will have to take positions from the crow in the future.",
        "He also stated that the President has become a hostage in the bud today."
      ],
